# VHS tape for the README demo GIF — https://github.com/charmbracelet/vhs
# Regenerate: task demo  (or: vhs docs/demo.tape)
Output docs/demo.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 15
Set Width 1080
Set Height 860
Set Padding 18
Set Theme "Dracula"

Hide
Type ".venv/bin/python scripts/demo.py"
Enter
Sleep 900ms
Show
Sleep 10s
